[div class=p 
	"Okay so I abuse this a lot in this run. I'll explain the glitch briefly. Basicially, if you have 1 legit card combo you can use every single card in that game as if you had it! (I don't know how Konami missed this, but whatever it's neat regardless.) You simply activate your DSS and before it's completely activated you go back to the DSS menu and select a card combo you don't have. There you have It, It's that simple.
	$LF
]div
